      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly, and all major mechanical systems are in solid working order. While there are some minor cosmetic imperfections and light interior wear consistent with its age, the car remains reliable and presents very well. It is a dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality vehicle that is ready to drive immediately.",
