    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require a dedicated owner or mechanic to return it to the road. The exterior shows substantial rust on the lower body panels and wheel arches, along with significant paint oxidation and several noticeable dents. Mechanically, the car is currently unreliable; the engine requires significant diagnostic work and likely a rebuild, and the suspension is quite worn. Inside, the cabin shows its age with torn upholstery, a cracked dashboard, and non-functional electronics, making this a true project car or a candidate for parts.",
