    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car, and it's honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid condition and has been super reliable for me over the years. It runs great, looks lovely, and is totally ready for its next big adventure! I\u2019ve taken wonderful care of it, so you\u2019re getting a fantastic vehicle that's ready to hit the road. Come by and take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you'll love it as much as I do!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
