    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3, a quintessential driver\u2019s car featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit excels with its individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing, providing a linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is paired with a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis remains tight, with a recent inspection of the rear subframe mounting points and a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment to ensure the valvetrain is within factory tolerances. Suspension components utilize the original MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear geometry, offering the communicative feedback these cars are known for. While showing minor signs of road use consistent with its age, the car remains an excellent candidate for a spirited daily or weekend canyon carvings.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
