    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a well-loved and meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and practicality. The exterior remains sharp, finished in a timeless coat that still holds a deep gloss, though you will find the expected minor stone chips from highway commuting consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the upholstery is free of rips or stains, and every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in its prime. I have kept a rigorous service schedule, recently completing a full fluid flush and brake pad replacement to ensure it\u2019s turn-key ready for its next owner. It shifts smoothly, idles quietly, and provides a confident, grounded ride. This isn't a showroom trailer queen, but a reliable, high-quality driver that has been treated with the respect it deserves. Includes a full set of floor mats and two sets of keys.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
